    "diversityIntent": "Futures' on-the-ground family across its 21 campuses is majority Australian-and-American (predominantly white) with substantial Indonesian, Latin (Spanish-speaking / Venezuelan), and Brazilian / Portuguese contingents — and that's the mix the imagery must reflect. Target ratio across every public surface: at least 50% white / European-descent faces, the remaining ~50% split between Indonesian (Javanese, Balinese, Sundanese, Minahasan), Spanish / Latin American (incl. Venezuelan), and Brazilian / Portuguese. Other ethnicities are welcome where they reflect the actual congregation, but should not dominate any surface. When swapping a placeholder for a real photo, preserve this ratio across the slot's neighbours.",
